{"tid":5190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左好多野都冇乜要求","createTime":"2016-11-26T18:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T15:43:32.000Z","uid":2179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7711ad26f0d51fdfc1bc05c5d6025b4aff6cdec5","tid":5190,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T18:59:03.000Z","msg":"以前想要一個天上有地下無嘅女神女朋友<br />\n大個左到依加只想要一個岩自己嘅安安穩穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分左手都半年，成日出街好多地方都有大家嘅回憶，每日都仲係好掛住佢想知佢生活過得好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好多野都冇得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都學識左珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f747b01c211bf1aecdea121dc1aad19e323fbfd","tid":5190,"uid":2179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636e65d114a9097b39c25d47fe56a1af0fe00182","tid":5190,"uid":12647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T19:45:09.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<br />\n幾靚都係假<br />\n一齊相處得舒服最緊要<br />\n曾經以為搵到個咁嘅人<br />\n原來對方只當我係水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e57990b326c5228dd44bfb2e5447ae9bc53763","tid":5190,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:59:09.000Z","msg":"開心先係最緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a4f4e6147fe959783a6640e407faf1339f3d71","tid":5190,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T23:59:36.000Z","msg":"曾經我都唔識珍惜 做左人渣翻唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9263e5ebd63424fa3ba59b389c54727ccdff315a","tid":5190,"uid":22312,"like":0,"dislike":0,